<ul>
  <li>
    <p><strong>Learning Objectives:</strong></p>

    <ul>
      <li>Understand the concept of an extensive game and its formal definition</li>
      <li>Become familiar with the concepts of   strategies in extensive games</li>
      <li>Learn how to solve for Nash equilibrium in extensive games</li>
      <li>Understand the meaning of an “empty threat” and how equilibrium refinement “subgame perfection” resolve this.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

